                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18210718-109-off628 t18210718-109-cd629"></join>, one silver watch, value 20 s.; one seal, value 1 s., and one key, value 4 s., the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18210718-109-victim1003" type="victimName">
                           Samuel 
                           Thomas
                        <interp inst="t18210718-109-victim1003" type="surname" value="Thomas"></interp>
